-- CPC Said to Buy 1.9 Million Barrels of Angolan, Congolese Oil for December
-- B y   Y u - h u a y   S u n
-- 2010-10-29T03:26:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-29/cpc-said-to-buy-1-9-million-barrels-of-oil-from-angola-congo-for-december.html
CPC Corp., Taiwan’s state oil
refiner, bought about 1.9 million barrels of Angolan and
Congolese crude for December loading from Total SA and Eni SpA,
according to a trader who participated in the tender.  Details of the refiner’s purchase are as follows:  To contact the reporters on this story:
